OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779883867
OL,3,CBody found in search for teenager who
OL,4,Cwent missing in Cheshire lake
OL,6,FA body has been found in a search for
OL,7,Fa 17-year-old boy who went missing
OL,8,Fafter going swimming in a lake in
OL,9,FCheshire.
OL,11,FPolice were called to reports of a
OL,12,Fmissing boy who was last seen in the
OL,13,Fwater at Pickmere Lake, Marston,
OL,14,FNorthwich at around 4.50pm on Tuesday
OL,15,F26 May.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
