PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779883867
OL,3,CBody found in search for teenager who
OL,4,Cwent missing in Cheshire lake
OL,6,FFormal identification has not yet
OL,7,Ftaken place, however, it is believed
OL,8,Fto be that of the missing teenager.
OL,9,FHis family has been informed and they
OL,10,Fare being supported by specially
OL,11,Ftrained officers.
OL,13,FThe death is not being treated as
OL,14,Fsuspicious.
OL,16,FPolice forces have issued warnings
OL,17,Fabout the potential risk to life from
OL,18,Fswimming in open water.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
