OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779883867
OL,3,CBody found in search for teenager who
OL,4,Cwent missing in Cheshire lake
OL,6,FIt is the second death in open water
OL,7,Fin the North West during the recent
OL,8,Fhot weather, after a body believed to
OL,9,Fbe of a 12-year-old boy was found in
OL,10,Fthe River Ribble in Ribchester.
OL,12,FOfficers carried out searches of the
OL,13,Farea supported by a police helicopter,
OL,14,FCheshire Fire and Rescue Service, and
OL,15,Fspecialist Underwater Search Teams.
OL,17,FThe boy was reported missing on
OL,18,FTuesday afternoon (27 May). Five fire
OL,19,Fengines, water rescue firefighters and
OL,20,Fa rescue boat were originally deployed
OL,21,Fto help find him.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779883867
OL,3,CBody found in search for teenager who
OL,4,Cwent missing in Cheshire lake
OL,6,FChief Inspector Jamie Lewis said:
OL,7,F"This was a young boy who had his
OL,8,Fentire life ahead of him. At what is
OL,9,Fan incredibly difficult time, our
OL,10,Fthoughts remain with the boy's family,
OL,11,Ffriends and everyone who knew him.
OL,13,F"While this is not the outcome we had
OL,14,Fhoped for, I would like to thank our
OL,15,Fcolleagues from the Constabulary,
OL,16,FCheshire Fire and Rescue Service and
OL,17,Fthe Underwater Search Team for their
OL,18,Fprofessionalism and commitment
OL,19,Fthroughout.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779883867
OL,3,CBody found in search for teenager who
OL,4,Cwent missing in Cheshire lake
OL,6,F"I would also like to thank the boy's
OL,7,Ffamily, friends and the local
OL,8,Fcommunity for their support during the
OL,9,Fsearch."
OL,11,FHe added: "Over the Bank Holiday
OL,12,Fweekend, we have sadly seen the very
OL,13,Freal dangers of swimming in open water.
OL,15,F"We understand that with the warm
OL,16,Fweather many people could be tempted
OL,17,Fto take a dip in open water to cool
OL,18,Foff, but residents must be aware of
OL,19,Fthe potential deadly consequences.
OL,26,@qD@HO]sD@KOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779883867
OL,3,CBody found in search for teenager who
OL,4,Cwent missing in Cheshire lake
OL,6,F"We don't want to discourage people
OL,7,Ffrom enjoying themselves near water,
OL,8,Fbut there can be hidden currents and
OL,9,Funseen dangers such as mud banks or
OL,10,Fitems under the water that a swimmer
OL,11,Fcan become caught on.
OL,13,F"While this location sits between two
OL,14,Flocal authority areas, the incident
OL,15,Ffalls within the Cheshire Constabulary
OL,16,Fpolicing area and is being led by us.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779883867
OL,3,CBody found in search for teenager who
OL,4,Cwent missing in Cheshire lake
OL,6,F"As such, it is our duty to inform and
OL,7,Fprotect the public of the potential
OL,8,Fdangers of such activity across the
OL,9,Fcounty. The message to our communities
OL,10,Fis a clear one, don't be tempted to
OL,11,Fput your life at risk by cooling off
OL,12,Fin open water.
OL,14,F"I would also like to remind those
OL,15,Fvisiting Pickmere Lake to park safely
OL,16,Fand responsibly.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779883867
OL,3,CBody found in search for teenager who
OL,4,Cwent missing in Cheshire lake
OL,6,F"While inconsiderate parking did not
OL,7,Fhinder the emergency response on this
OL,8,Foccasion, in incidents such as this,
OL,9,Femergency services require immediate
OL,10,Faccess, and poorly parked vehicles
OL,11,Fcould significantly delay our ability
OL,12,Fto respond."
OL,14,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,15,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,16,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,17,Four region.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@LO]
